metadata.name: lightly enlighten
metadata.description:
Remember that enlightenment is not a push and it will come to you. Be light. 

This digital artwork contains an augmented reality layer capturing the creation process. AR viewable with the free Artivive app.

This one of a kind rare digital art piece is part of Matt Semke (catswilleatyou)'s enormous and historic body of work. Original art created in 2021.
